---

<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
	<h2
		style="font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Montserrat Variable', sans-serif;"
		class="text-pretty text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl"
	>
		Where 'No Code' Ends,<br />RPTrainor Excellence Begins
	</h2>
	<p
		style="font-family: 'Delicious Handrawn', fallback-font, sans-serif;"
